title: Journeyman Interview
Application Type: I applied through an employee referral. The process took 1+ week. I interviewed at Carpenters Union Local 254 (Philadelphia, PA)
Interview Descriptions: Testing cycle in May in which you will take a math test to get into the carpenters then attend a four year school to determine if you can handle the work. During school you work 4 days out of the weeek and are off during the summer.
